reviews.text:
As a fan of soda and floral vapes, this one was right up my alley. I would have never thought to combine the two! This turns out to be a nice, refreshing summer time vape. The honeysuckle creates a nice mellow floral base, and is lifted up by the elderflower for a prominent but not overbearing floral. I like the mix of citrus soda + lemon lime; citrus soda is great but needs a little bit of support to really push it in the direction of soda and the lemon lime does that. At first I thought the pear might be a bit high, but it does wonders in accenting the citrus flavors and adding some juicy sweetness that a soda needs. Top it off with some ice and it's delicious! I might bump the ws-23 to 0.75% but that's just a personal preference (I like 'em cold!). &#xD;
&#xD;
I think this is a great floral recipe for those to try who are interested in florals but don't necessarily want to vape "flowers". Excellent job!
